{"tid":1707904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反撚正都要比人銼 我覺得所有人都要出街食生果","createTime":"2019-11-11T12:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T14:58:39.000Z","uid":167938,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f24c3aee2bd9807d381767505c587fe77891d7f","tid":1707904,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:01:49.000Z","msg":"係非常合理 2014 已經由廢老證實<br />\n出街湯橙係好正常<br />\n<br />\n點解我地唔出街切生果<br />\n一人一個橙？<br />\n<br />\n有維他命c又好食<br />\n<br />\n班狗五個月以黎衝埋黎都好似唔驚死咁<br />\n你打爆年青人個賢 插狗賢 兩邊<br />\n頸放血 手腳界一界都已經走得<br />\n<br />\n氣油彈 比你燒到黑哂 佢都唔死得<br />\n湯橙係唔係應該用刀湯 ？<br />\n而唔係用火燒？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XRLaPoz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXRLaPoz.jpg&h=8b5715a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6abe2a4a4be0586516654ee9339af33bbfac7c50","tid":1707904,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"狗殺人<br />\n我地仲可以放軟對腳？"},{"pid":"c848a3255cacebc2943c7eef2a8211a1ca87469b","tid":1707904,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f25072a038ed7f9ee5957f031752de66e0d72c8","tid":1707904,"uid":157152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c848a3255cacebc2943c7eef2a8211a1ca87469b","tid":1707904,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:33:24.000Z","msg":"睇唔明你講乜"},{"pid":"1162c4a885ced55b9a10ffe06d06e2744c3d2387","tid":1707904,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:36:35.000Z","msg":"我自己就鐘意畫畫<br />\n所以隨身帶幾枝素描筆都唔過份丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1795454968ffa3b5f6f82e0f34f7783a0b5d4723","tid":1707904,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:42:27.000Z","msg":"大家一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p